{"tid":1388494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上網查咗陪審團制度的資料，大家入嚟討論下","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T00:35:06.000Z","uid":71237,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf79460405478d9f75364156a292f2b9b6d1315","tid":1388494,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:03:15.000Z","msg":"今日我上網查咗關於陪審團制度的資料，同大家講下我查到啲咩。<br />\n只有我唔太熟悉法律，如果有錯歡迎大家指正。<br />\n<br />\nQ1. 係咪所有案件都會有陪審團？<br />\nA1. 唔係。控方可以揀案件喺區院審定係高院審。<br />\n如果係區院審，最多判七年，但係無陪審團制度，高院先至有陪審團制度。<br />\n但係喺區院判咗之後就可以向高院上訴，但到時義士們已經受咗好多苦。<br />\n<br />\nQ2. 咩人先可以擔任陪審團？<br />\nA2. 自己去維基睇，下面有link。<br />\n值得留意的係去到成立陪審團的時候，控辯雙方都有無限次機會可以提出理由反對陪審員參與案件。例如你比人發現你大大聲喺網上講過要運用「陪審團否決權」去釋放義士，控方就有理由去反對你擔任陪審員。<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">支持「陪審團否決權」的朋友，你地唔好咁揚</span>。<br />\n如果係自己人，做咗陪審團之後自然會諗到依樣嘢，根本唔洗你地提。<br />\n如果唔係自己人，睇到你呼籲用否決權救義士，只會鬧你妨礙司法公正。<br />\n你們大大聲周圍講「陪審團否決權」，對成件事係無任何幫助。<br />\n同埋任何人企圖在法庭以外影響陪審員的決定，可能會妨礙司法公正（依個我唔sure，等熟悉法律的巴打解答）。<br />\n頭先我喺連登仲見到有人話要喺連儂牆宣傳「陪審團否決權」，我勸你真係唔好。<br />\n<br />\n「陪審團否決權」係重要，但只可以由有幸被選中嘅人安靜地去做。<br />\n表面上，你只可以根據在庭上聽取的證供而對案件的事實作出裁斷。<br />\n你唔可以因為自己的政治立場而影響你的決定。<br />\n實際上係點？你只可以將實際的理由永遠永遠收埋喺心底，將秘密帶入墳墓。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n曾焯文 - 區院陪審團？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1051567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1051567&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=c5c34b96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1051567&h=481b7944\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1051567</a><br />\n<br />\n陪審團<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/jury/jury.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fzh%2Fjury%2Fjury.html&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=a9682a0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/jury/jury.html</a><br />\n<br />\n維基百科 - 香港陪審團制度<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港陪審團制度\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%9C%98%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=d998cc81\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港陪審團制度</a>"},{"pid":"d0edba9e22eea128e7b6ae33cf6586d3ddf27ed0","tid":1388494,"uid":36845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a12ab9612e25f93cb85789b5f863f6de9fd6d98","tid":1388494,"uid":285851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"6f6f848d532ffcc5932ea13a963dd4f8e5e713af","tid":1388494,"uid":285851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:06:42.000Z","msg":"瘋狂推"},{"pid":"d14ed242464b496348b62ed519d28af26489409b","tid":1388494,"uid":285851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再講啦"},{"pid":"a5ac43c5757cd6d79426bae40f288a6ccb7c8a95","tid":1388494,"uid":285851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c0b95ac2f71cd68f265e06e910fc62450c14229","tid":1388494,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"多謝你呀<br />\n推"},{"pid":"cd471ec1bb7c1919208e537d8f836073851ea12f","tid":1388494,"uid":285851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67847de814dc2966662816f5f24e88edcacb5ed8","tid":1388494,"uid":285851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a0008c329ac85724845ed02711dd4f8fa5e1c1a","tid":1388494,"uid":285851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"真係唔好繼續講"},{"pid":"29edf69ac9775ddaf8a1142d330e0e16576c42e8","tid":1388494,"uid":285851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid"