.hk/zh/jury/jury.html</a><br />\n<br />\n維基百科 - 香港陪審團制度<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港陪審團制度\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%9C%98%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=d998cc81\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港陪審團制度</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"理論上佢宣傳用陪審團權力否決應該無罪，因為陪審團係prefer開庭前中立，開庭期間隔離，亦唔可以用任何通訊器材，最多要求娛樂係電影/音樂。而且陪審團身份保密，你輿論壓力再高，都影響唔到佢哋人身安全，所以任何庭外宣傳都難以影響法庭立場。"},{"pid":"73250248cf40f728718195b6fdf0efd4a284a499","tid":1388494,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"你班撚樣咪撚再講陪審員呀！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388453</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d61a82f2ad1ced6f0236a4f2e340cc9f25985e6a","tid":1388494,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:11:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"355fa0c4432dde869ddd6f67ae21a170f6423d7b","tid":1388494,"uid":142233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90bd622d0b58f4e8838575cadc198270d97546ee","tid":1388494,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理論上佢宣傳用陪審團權力否決應該無罪，因為陪審團係prefer開庭前中立，開庭期間隔離，亦唔可以用任何通訊器材，最多要求娛樂係電影/音樂。而且陪審團身份保密，你輿論壓力再高，都影響唔到佢哋人身安全，所以任何庭外宣傳都難以影響法庭立場。</blockquote><br />\n如果好多人喺連登大力宣傳「陪審團否決權」，到時控方律師問你有冇上過連登。你答有，控方就有理由去反對你做陪審團。到時可能你想做都無得做。<br />\n<br />\n就算你做咗，成功判到義士無罪，但事後比人踢爆你大大聲講過自己係睇政治立場去決定，而唔係跟證供而決定。<br />\n律政司都可能要求重審，你自己都可能有法律責任。<br />\n（雖然我唔太sure，但我都係睇唔出有任何理由要大肆宣揚。）"},{"pid":"61258f7bd3f47da2a9f89a49b1b3a2e813df1ebf","tid":1388494,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:15:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"833bdb122bf7448618b8ef460272196233937e09","tid":1388494,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb03550dfaa906c9c133f32bc6bab843c7f027a4","tid":1388494,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"12f9ee9684d1ed4feb2d4fab0e3ddb06feef852f","tid":1388494,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"833bdb122bf7448618b8ef460272196233937e09","tid":1388494,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:29:21.000Z","msg":"就嚟收架啦"},{"pid":"df85c0a01fba094285f99d87aeef3bb5a741a8d4","tid":1388494,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5e642a94c65a6c541ff1fbba6b71af20aac52f","tid":1388494,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:00:53.000Z","msg":"剛剛有人更正我，就算上訴到高院，多數都係拗法律觀點，係唔會有陪審團。"},{"pid":"d3675b7591e1883e20537eab97021a0deb8b1db6","tid":1388494,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d389db9584406646b5097d84088fdd467df8af6e","tid":1388494,"uid":1247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:47:41.000Z","msg":"想知 佢問你有無上過連登時 可唔可以答無?"}]}